	<section>
		<div class="container py-5">
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-md-12 pb-2">
					<h3 class="display-5 text-center">Architectural Marvel</h3>
					<p class=" lead text-center">
						The resort's architecture seamlessly blends modern amenities with
						eco-friendly design principles. The expansive glass windows not only offer panoramic views
						of the azure ocean but also allow natural light to flood the interior spaces. The
						accommodations are designed to evoke a sense of calmness, with each room offering a private
						balcony or terrace for guests to enjoy the soothing sea breeze.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-3 py-sm-3"><img src="~/images/about-page/about-5.jpg" alt="" class="img-fluid"></div>
				<div class="col-md-3 py-sm-3"><img src="~/images/about-page/about-6.jpg" alt="" class="img-fluid"></div>
				<div class="col-md-3 py-sm-3"><img src="~/images/about-page/about-7.jpg" alt="" class="img-fluid"></div>
				<div class="col-md-3 py-sm-3"><img src="~/images/about-page/about-8.jpg" alt="" class="img-fluid"></div>
